1. What problem does this solve?
Many contact forms rely on servers, databases, and complex backend infrastructure. This project demonstrates how to build a secure, scalable contact form using a fully serverless architecture on AWS.

2. What architecture did you choose — and why?

You already have this:

Serverless (Lambda + API Gateway + SES)

Event-driven

No servers to manage

Cost-efficient

